288
00:24:23,220 --> 00:24:24,877
The royal villa at Wessex.

289
00:24:27,189 --> 00:24:28,190
Wessex.

290
00:24:32,332 --> 00:24:33,472
Ecbert.

291
00:24:35,197 --> 00:24:36,233
Yes.

292
00:24:37,234 --> 00:24:38,373
Ecbert.

293
