328
00:27:22,848 --> 00:27:24,539
might have understood
that by now.

329
00:28:40,615 --> 00:28:44,792
Ubbe, Ubbe, Ubbe!

330
00:28:44,826 --> 00:28:48,450
Ubbe, Ubbe, Ubbe!

331
00:28:54,111 --> 00:28:56,769
You see, you'’re famous.

332
00:28:57,666 --> 00:29:02,430
Ubbe, Ubbe,
Ubbe!

333
