out of here,

456
00:37:35,460 --> 00:37:37,289
then we will do it together.

457
00:37:39,671 --> 00:37:41,397
And if the odds
are against us,

458
00:37:41,431 --> 00:37:45,228
then it will make me happy
to die with you.

459
00:37:49,784 --> 00:37:51,821
