a woman say that.

460
00:37:52,166 --> 00:37:53,616
Oh.

461
00:37:53,650 --> 00:37:54,755
Everyone can be wrong.

462
00:37:54,789 --> 00:37:55,790
Ubbe.

463
00:37:55,825 --> 00:37:56,826
Even you.

464
00:37:58,621 --> 00:38:00,933
Two of us want
to avail ourselves

465
00:38:00,968 --> 00:38:02,832
